[color=Gray]Ensure that all parts of this form are accurate and honest to the greatest extent of your knowledge. After completing this form, it should be turned into the Quartermaster for review. If they approve and stamp your application, it must be taken to the Head of Personnel's office to be processed. An accepted application requires the Head of Personnel stamp and either the Quartermaster stamp or Captain stamp to be valid. A Central Command stamp can also validate this form.[/color]
